      ],
      "content": "NetworkTopologyStrategy see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Data Replication<ept id=\"p1\">](http://www.datastax.com/documentation/cassandra/2.0/cassandra/architecture/architectureDataDistributeReplication_c.html)</ept> in Cassandra documentation for more information"
    },
    {
      "content": "Understands the deployment topology and places replicas on nodes so that all the replicas don’t end up on the same rack",
      "pos": [
