      ],
      "content": "GossipingPropertyFileSnitch see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Snitches<ept id=\"p1\">](http://www.datastax.com/documentation/cassandra/2.0/cassandra/architecture/architectureSnitchesAbout_c.html)</ept> in Cassandra documentation for more information"
    },
    {
      "content": "NetworkTopologyStrategy uses a concept of snitch to understand the topology.",
      "pos": [
        9063,
