    },
    {
      "content": "Both regions have similar network architecture in terms of “web” and “data” subnets; Azure networking allows the creation of as many subnets as needed and apply ACLs as needed by network security.",
      "pos": [
        14148,
        14344
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "While designing the cluster topology inter data center communication latency and the economic impact of the network traffic need to be considered.",
      "pos": [
