      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Distributed deployments need to be aware of the cluster topology impact on throughput and high availability.",
      "pos": [
        14548,
        14656
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The RF and Consistency Level need to be selected in such way that the quorum doesn’t depend on the availability of all the data centers.",
      "pos": [
        14657,
        14793
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For a system that needs high consistency, a LOCAL_QUORUM for consistency level (for reads and writes) will make sure that the local reads and writes are satisfied from the local nodes while data is replicated asynchronously to the remote data centers.",
